high_descs: Turn around and look at the shelves.
Pick up the mug.
Turn around and walk past the table to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge on the shelf above the tomato and close the door. Wait a moment, and take the mug out.
Turn around and veer right to the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the coffee maker drip area.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around to face the wooden shelves.
Pick up the white cup next to the grey bottle.
Turn around, walk towards the dishwasher and then turn right towards the fridge.
Place the cup on the top shelf of the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn around, walk to the oven, and then turn right to find the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and face the wooden shelves.
Pick up the white mug next to the white bottle.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the right side of the room.
Place the mug in the fridge on the top shelf, close the door, wait a few seconds, take the mug out of the fridge and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the coffee pot on the right.
Place the mug in the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: To chill a mug and put it in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and face the shelf.
Pick up the coffee cup.
Turn around and walk all the way to the other side of the room, then turn right and head towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the coffee cup inside, close the door, wait a bit, open the door, and then take out the coffee cup.
Turn around and walk all the way to the counter, then turn right and face the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and face the shelves.
Pick up the white mug.
Turn around, take a few steps and veer right to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge. Wait a moment and take it out.
Turn around and walk to the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the correct place in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to stand in front of the brown shelving unit.
Pick up the white mug from the top shelf.
Cross the room and turn right to stand in front of the silver fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the mug on the top shelf, close the door, open the door, and remove the mug.
Turn and move to the counter so you're in front of the coffee maker and toaster.
Place the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug from the shelving unit to the coffee maker.
